"1069","of compliance with the policies or procedures may deteriorate."
"1070","A deficiency in internal control over financial reporting exists"
"1071","when the design or operation of a control does not allow"
"1072","management or employees, in the normal course of performing their"
"1073","assigned functions, to prevent or detect misstatements on a"
"1074","timely basis.  A material weakness is a deficiency, or a"
